        "content": [
          {
            "text": "A five-minute tapping practice for the feeling that money earned by a partner is not really yours to spend. The script works through the guilt and the smallness underneath. It moves toward a clear sense that the money is yours too, even without earning it directly.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "New to tapping? Read ",
